Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Boost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
